{"type": "article", "id": 32077, "title": "无论什么灵感，这本笔记本都能记下来｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-09-11T23:06:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 32650, "name": "YOU+MORE！"}, {"id": 32651, "name": "Intenxiv Studio"}, {"id": 18007, "name": "Felissimo"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 18, "praise_count": 421, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160912001800kvUC6GsWuPMegLcl.gif", "contents": "<p class=\"\">          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>SketchyNotebook by Tim Tu et al.</h3><p>台湾设计师 Tim Tu 和许多创意工作者一样，会在文思泉涌时用笔记本记录灵感。当他发现市面上并没有符合不同需求的笔记本之后，他带领团队设计了这款名为 SketchyNotebook 的多功能笔记本套装。套装内包括笔记本和为不同使用需求专门设计的 PVC 塑料模版，包括文字工作者使用的横式、为平面设计师量身定制的格状、App 设计师的手机样式模版等等，使用时只要将模版垫在空白页面下即可。笔记本本身也经过精心设计，不管打开哪一页都是平坦的 180 度，没有一般笔记本打开后的凹凸不平感。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/timtwo/new-sketchynotebook-series-creatives-all-in-one-no\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 18 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912001844QsWalJTg5FNiG8HK.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.445588\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912001845Rhcis8nMdpS2Dx9P.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.458824\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912001845gWQAaMbCuilwhUIE.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361765\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912001844i5RobeS8A67KJHhP.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664706\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912001846Mptg3Y9k2QS0cVIr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.645588\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912001850e9LoYPvq3yBzfhMt.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664706\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>GARY by Sebastian Max</h3><p>来自英国伦敦的设计师 Sebastian Max 和不少人一样会为了防止耳机线绕成一团特意使用卷线器，当他发现现有的产品并不耐用且也少有时尚的外观后，他决定自己设计一款实用又好看的卷线器。在尝试了多种材质之后，这款名为 GARY 的卷线器诞生了：它长 6 厘米，宽 2 厘米，可以轻松地放在口袋里随身携带。卷线和抽线的过程就好像拉动卷尺那样，非常方便。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1055129788/gary-earphones-and-cables-best-friend\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 9 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912002247jm3blYONZKJcrMEL.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912002237rhFzbHMlGYwesO3A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.457353\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912002238c07YMjxqHF5kbvOX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662739\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912002239MgFbRO6jsGaySJh2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.819118\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Fidget Cube by Antsy Labs</h3><p>当你感到焦虑的时候是不是忍不住做一些小动作？最近，由美国丹佛的 McLachlan 兄弟创立的 <a href=\"http://www.antsylabs.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Antsy Labs</a> 就参考了人们会做的一些小动作，设计了这款名为 Fidget Cube 的减压小玩具。它的外形或许会让你联想到骰子，只不过它的六个面对应的是六种供人摆弄以释放压力的小物件，包括按钮、摇杆、开关、可触摸的凹面、滚齿轮以及小转盘。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/2015098713/fidget-cube-a-vinyl-desk-toy\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 19 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912002154tyL7eduE1f5aSHV3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912002155lbLucevCzkXmORnB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912002156nOik3Py1MUK9X8sa.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.526667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912002206kUzKg0nL7GIseCjM.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912002157wt1U4BmKCvQDLhRn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667158\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Bunny Box by YOU+MORE！</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.felissimo.co.jp/youmore/\" rel=\"nofollow\">YOU+MORE！</a>是日本 <a href=\"http://www.felissimo.co.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">FELISSIMO</a> 公司旗下的一个品牌，专营围绕着动植物为主题设计的家居产品。这款兔子模样的收纳包就是来自 YOU+MORE！的新品，连包袋的部分都设计成了兔子的两只耳朵。当你将东西打包、绑好带子放进盒子后，这只“饱餐一顿”的小动物就成了能让房间的气氛明亮起来的装饰，用这种可爱的方式进行收纳似乎心情都会变得好起来。这是它的<a href=\"http://gcl.felissimo.jp/goods_en_jpy_49252.html?gnrid=322\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 2678 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912002112sOeIbKAwVdQMk1G8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912002117UinfWr1FRx05gkMb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609120021145EeHKZjI9cdsFVhS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912002122eEDcP0CsXmMALGZO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Inchworm Shezlong by Alexandra Knyazevoy</h3><p>Alexandra Knyazevoy 在莫斯科国立斯特罗加诺夫艺术工业大学（Stroganov Moscow State University of Arts and Industry）学习家具设计，这件名为 Inchworm 的躺椅是她毕业作品的一部分。白色的金属支架是 Knyazevoy 参照尺蠖一曲一伸的移动方式设计的，上面放置了一张与支架一节节对应的羽绒垫，躺上去似乎格外舒适惬意。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912001947i5mhUpkwqBL4WnFA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609120019498G9loUnNcx5QApWm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912001947bAZlxuJeUGK8hHIR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912001945BabSuAl7TcGnq86L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912001948F9soLuICHPzErJQG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912001950WFdVZsgBiSum7jCc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Cockoo wall-clock by Intenxiv Studio</h3><p>既然鸟儿是生活在树洞里的，为什么布谷鸟钟不能被设计成树的样子呢？抱着这一想法，韩国 <a href=\"http://www.intenxiv.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Intenxiv Studio</a> 打造了这款颠覆传统布谷鸟钟设计的挂钟 <a href=\"http://www.intenxiv.com/bird-clock\" rel=\"nofollow\">Cockoo wall-clock</a>：“树干”斜切般的横截面是它的钟面，整个挂钟只有分针和“树洞”内的布谷鸟涂上了蓝色，与白色搭配看上去非常清爽。和其他布谷鸟钟一样，它每个小时也会准时从洞内伸出来报时，外观上更具有现代感。</p><p class=\"\">顺便一提，记得挂高一点。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609120018103lVJ8Fn2PdLSf6Ie.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912001811j8VkSGuNoYQxUynr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912001810fI6TlqCjmvOFAiDh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912001811Vv9IbnYGycOL0Shd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609120018128tOAfmxkzRYyXoEM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}